---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Lancelot" description="About Lancelot and this AI learning journey">
  <main id="main-content" class="container">
    <article class="page-content">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Lancelot. I'm on a journey to learn about AI - what it can do,
        how it works, and how I can use it in my own projects.
      </p>
      <p>
        This website is where I document everything I learn along the way.
        Think of it as a public notebook: sometimes messy, always honest.
        Beyond AI, I also share more general thoughts, interests, and things I find along the road.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you're curious about AI too, I hope you'll find something useful here.
        The best way to reach me is by
        <a href="mailto:lancelot.brun@gmail.com">email</a> or
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lancelotbrun/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
      </p>

      <section class="interests">
        <h2>Things I want to learn</h2>
        <p class="interests-note">If you know anything about these topics or have recommendations, I'd love to <a href="mailto:lancelot.brun@gmail.com">hear from you</a>.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>History</li>
          <li>Learning the guitar</li>
          <li>Being able to recognize birds</li>
          <li>Cultivating my own vegetables</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .page-content h1 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .page-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .interests {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .interests h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .interests-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .interests ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .interests li {
    padding: 0.35rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
</style>
